                            <h4>Discover Interesting projects and people to populate your personal news feed.</h4>
                            <p>Your news feed helps you keep up with recent activity on repositories you <a href=""
                                    class="text-decoration-none">watch</a> or <a href=""
                                    class="text-decoration-none">star</a> and people you <a href=""
                                    class="text-decoration-none">follow</a>.</p>
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" id="mainButton">Explore GitHub</button>
                        </div>
                        <div id="bottomBlurb" class="mt-4 text-muted mb-5">
                            <p><span><img class="avatar" src="/icons/bulb.png" alt=""></span><b>ProTip!</b> The feed shows you events from people you <a
                                    class="text-decoration-none" href="">follow</a> and repositories you <a
                                    class="text-decoration-none" href="">watch</a> or <a class="text-decoration-none"
                                    href="">star</a>.
                            </p>
                            <p><span>
                                <svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" data-view-component="true">
                                    <path stroke="#979A9C" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.002 2.725a.75.75 0 01.797-.699C8.79 2.42 13.58 7.21 13.974 13.201a.75.75 0 11-1.497.098 10.502 10.502 0 00-9.776-9.776.75.75 0 01-.7-.798zM2 13a1 1 0 112 0 1 1 0 01-2 0zm.84-5.95a.75.75 0 00-.179 1.489c2.509.3 4.5 2.291 4.8 4.8a.75.75 0 101.49-.178A7.003 7.003 0 002.838 7.05z""></path>
